#lets find the categorialfeatures
list_1=list(data.columns)
list_cate=[]
for i in list_1:
    if data[i].dtype=='object':
        list_cate.append(i)
from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelEncoder
le=LabelEncoder()
for i in list_cate:
    data[i]=le.fit_transform(data[i])
data
